### ============================================================
### Chocolatería del Paraíso – API Tests (REST Client / IntelliJ)
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  CATEGORÍAS
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [1] Listar categorías activas (paginado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories?page=0&size=5&sort=name
Accept: application/json

###

### [2] Listar categorías filtrando por nombre
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories?name=Amargo&page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

###

### [3] Obtener categoría por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1
Accept: application/json

###

### [4] Crear nueva categoría
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Chocolates Artesanales",
  "description": "Elaborados a mano por nuestros maestros chocolateros",
  "active": true
}

###

### [5] Actualizar categoría
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Chocolates Amargos Premium",
  "description": "Selección especial de cacaos con 70% o más de pureza",
  "active": true
}

###

### [6] Eliminar categoría (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/6
Accept: application/json

###


### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  CLIENTES
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [7] Listar clientes activos (paginado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers?page=0&size=10&sort=lastName
Accept: application/json

###

### [8] Buscar clientes por nombre/email
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers?search=valentina&page=0&size=5
Accept: application/json

###

### [9] Obtener cliente por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1
Accept: application/json

###

### [10] Crear nuevo cliente
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Florencia",
  "lastName": "Peralta",
  "email": "florencia.peralta@email.com",
  "phone": "11-2233-4455",
  "address": "Tucumán 890, Buenos Aires",
  "active": true
}

###

### [11] Actualizar cliente
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Valentina",
  "lastName": "Rodríguez",
  "email": "valentina.rodriguez@email.com",
  "phone": "11-9999-0000",
  "address": "Av. Callao 1500, CABA",
  "active": true
}

###

### [12] Eliminar cliente (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/5
Accept: application/json

###


### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  PRODUCTOS (Chocolates)
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [13] Listar todos los chocolates activos (paginado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?page=0&size=5&sort=name
Accept: application/json

###

### [14] Filtrar por nombre
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?name=Trufa&page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

###

### [15] Filtrar por categoría (Bombones y Trufas = id 4)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?categoryId=4&page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

###

### [16] Filtrar por nombre Y categoría
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?name=Barra&categoryId=1&page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

###

### [17] Lista completa para selector (sin paginación)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/all-active
Accept: application/json

###

### [18] Obtener producto por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1
Accept: application/json

###

### [19] Crear nuevo chocolate
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Trufa de Maracuyá con Chocolate Amargo",
  "description": "Ganache tropical de maracuyá cubierto en chocolate oscuro 65%",
  "price": 360.00,
  "stock": 40,
  "categoryId": 4,
  "active": true
}

###

### [20] Actualizar precio y stock de un chocolate
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Trufa de Chocolate Amargo 70%",
  "description": "Trufa artesanal de cacao venezolano 70%, con cobertura de polvo de cacao",
  "price": 380.00,
  "stock": 55,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "active": true
}

###

### [21] Eliminar producto (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/10
Accept: application/json

###


### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  VENTAS / PEDIDOS
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [22] Listar todas las ventas (paginado, orden descendente por fecha)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sales?page=0&size=10&sort=saleDate,desc
Accept: application/json

###

### [23] Filtrar ventas CONFIRMADAS
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sales?status=CONFIRMED&page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

###

### [24] Filtrar ventas CANCELADAS
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sales?status=CANCELLED&page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

###

### [25] Obtener detalle de una venta
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sales/1
Accept: application/json

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### [26] CHECKOUT – Venta con múltiples chocolates (CASO FELIZ)
###
###  Cliente: Valentina Rodríguez (id=1)
###  Productos:
###    - Trufa de Chocolate Amargo 70%   (id=1) x2  → $700.00
###    - Bombón de Avellana              (id=3) x3  → $870.00
###    - Barra Sin Azúcar 70%            (id=9) x1  → $390.00
###  Total esperado: $1,960.00
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sales/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "notes": "Embalaje especial para regalo. Sin azúcar adicional.",
  "details": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 2 },
    { "productId": 3, "quantity": 3 },
    { "productId": 9, "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### [27] CHECKOUT – Venta simple (Matías González, 1 item)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sales/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 2,
  "notes": "Entrega en sucursal Rosario.",
  "details": [
    { "productId": 5, "quantity": 5 }
  ]
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### [28] CHECKOUT – Error: Stock insuficiente
###  Se solicitan 999 unidades de Trufa (stock ≈ 50)
###  Respuesta esperada: HTTP 409 Conflict con InsufficientStockException
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sales/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 3,
  "details": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 999 }
  ]
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### [29] CHECKOUT – Error: Validación (detalle vacío)
###  Respuesta esperada: HTTP 400 Bad Request (validation error)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sales/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "details": []
}

###

### [30] Cancelar venta (revierte stock)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/sales/1/cancel
Accept: application/json

###
